","tier","to","touch","translations","typically","unpaid","uptime","us","will","with","work","workforce","writing","you"],"pipeline":["trimmer"]}, "docs": {"11":{"title":"Support","content":"Support\nYou can find more detailed technical information and Architectural Decision Records (ADRs) on our Confluence pages, or in our GitHub repository.\nStatus\nService uptime information is available on the Pingdom status page.\nAny live incidents will typically be dealt with and communicated over Slack.\nIncident reviews are posted on Confluence.\nContact us\nFor any other questions, feel free to get in touch with us by:\n\n\nDropping a message on our Slack channel,\nSending us an Email, or\nCreating a GitHub issue in our repository\n\n","url":"/support.html"},"12":{"title":"About","content":"About\nA collection of small, domain-focused integrations to support HMPPS Digital services that need to interact with\nprobation data. Typically, these integration services will perform translations between HMPPS and Delius domain\nconcepts, and are responsible for:\n\n\npublishing REST endpoints to read existing data from the Delius database\nlistening for HMPPS Domain Event messages and writing data into the Delius database\n\nServices\nFollow these links to find out more about each of our integration services.\n\n\nApproved Premises And Delius\nApproved Premises And OASys\nCustody Key Dates And Delius\nMake Recall Decisions And Delius\nManage POM Cases And Delius\nOffender Events And Delius\nPerson Search Index From Delius\nPre-Sentence Reports To Delius\nPrison Case Notes To Probation\nPrison Custody Status To Delius\nRisk Assessment Scores To Delius\nTier To Delius\nUnpaid Work And Delius\nWorkforce Allocations To Delius\n^ add new projects here\n\n","url":"/"}}}